---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

    <div
        class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-8 w-full my-auto"
    >
        <!-- Wrapper to keep the max width -->
        <div class="max-w-4xl w-full flex flex-col gap-12">
            <!-- Top Section: Title & Summary -->
            <main>
                <h1
                    class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-10 text-black"
                >
                    ungkuamer.
                </h1>

                <div
                    class="space-y-6 xs:text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-lg text-gray-800 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    <p class="font-bold text-black text-lg md:text-2xl leading-snug">
                        I build high-performance web systems and AI applications that help businesses ship faster, reduce hosting overhead, and scale without technical debt.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Instead of letting you get bogged down in tech stack debates or server management, I handle the entire engineering lifecycle. You get fast, production-ready systems designed to solve immediate business bottlenecks while remaining maintainable and cheap to run as you grow.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Whether launching an interactive SaaS MVP, setting up an AI pipeline, or auditing code to slash cloud expenses, my priority is the same: delivering maximum business value with the cleanest, most reliable technology possible.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Dotted lines -->
                    <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-4 pt-4">
                        <div
                            class="border-b-4 border-dotted border-gray-300 w-full"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
    </div>
